{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-wangfeng-008__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-wangfeng-008", "source_id": "guofeng-wangfeng-008__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "poem", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·王風·008.1", "text_original": "彼采葛兮，一日不見，如三月兮。\n彼采蕭兮，一日不見，如三秋兮。\n彼采艾兮，一日不見，如三歲兮。", "text_normalized": "彼采葛兮，一日不見，如三月兮。\n彼采蕭兮，一日不見，如三秋兮。\n彼采艾兮，一日不見，如三歲兮。", "notes": "采葛 Chinese poem 1."}
